description._content: Collection: Human Ecology Historical Photographs Title: Faculty of the department of home economics inJune 1916. Seated on the ground are Claribel Nye (left) and Anna Hunn. In the second row, from left, are Annette Warner, Helen BinkerdYoung, Flora Rose and Martha Van Rensselaer. In the third row, from left are Smith, Winifred Moses, Mary Henry, Bertha Titsworth, Edith Fleming, Beulah Blackmore, Frances Vinton, Helen Canon, Lucille Brewer and Helen Knowlton. Collection #23-2-749, item AP-P-04 Div. Rare & Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library Persistent URI: http://hdl.handle.net/1813.001/5wj9 There are no known U.S. copyright restrictions on this image.
